summary: This mod replaces the original coin with a coin of John II Casimir (former king of Poland) from 1668. New bump map is also included. And yes, this coin looks really amazing.
descriptionHtml:
This mod replaces the original coin with a coin of John II Casimir (former king of Poland) from 1668. New bump map is also included. And yes, this coin looks really amazing.

Installation: copy my Data folder to your main game directory.
author: The Iceman
